==Finnish==

===Verb===
'''nussia'''

# ''(vulgar, with the object in the [[partitive case]])'' To [[fuck]], screw, have sex.
#: Sinähän et '''nussi''' mun siskoani! &mdash; ''"You will not '''fuck''' my sister!"''
# ''(vulgar, with the object in the genitive-accusative case)'' To [[steal]], snatch, [[feck]].
#: Kuka vittu on '''nussinut''' mun lompakkoni? &mdash; ''"Who the fuck has '''snatched''' my wallet?"''

